# Project Technical Stack

## General

- **Package Manager**: pnpm, npm, bun
- **Code Quality**: ESLint, Prettier
- **Testing**: Jest
- **Containerization**: Docker
- **Deployment**: Vercel, Google Cloud Run
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions, GitLab CI

## Frontend

- **Language**: TypeScript/TSX, CSS
- **Framework**: React.js (Vite.js), Next.js, Vue, Angular
- **Router**: TanStack Router, Next.js App Router
- **Data Fetching**: TanStack Query, Electric SQL
- **State Management**: Zustand, React Context
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS, Material UI, Framer Motion
- **Validation**: Zod, React Hook Form
- **Error Handling**: Effect, try/catch
- **Internationalization**: React i18next, Next Intl
- **Observability**: PostHog
- **Other Dependencies**: Lucide React, ShadCN UI, @alewin/useWorker

## Backend

- **Language**: TypeScript, SQL
- **Runtime**: Node.js, Bun
- **Framework**: Fastify, Nest.js, Express.js
- **Database**: PostgreSQL
- **ORM**: Drizzle, Prisma
- **Validation**: Zod
- **Authentication**: Auth0
- **Error Handling**: Effect, try/catch
- **API**: REST, tRPC, Next.js API Routes
- **Queue/Jobs**: BullMQ
- **Caching**: Redis, Upstash
- **Logging**: Pino
- **Documentation**: OpenAPI/Swagger
- **Other Dependencies**: OpenRouter API, Exa API
